{"tid":1960741,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"自選十大最喜歡的港劇","createTime":"2020-04-06T10:40:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T08:54:14.000Z","uid":325346,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"b996633592566c92993913f8b9a8d88ef4fb215a","tid":1960741,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:40:49.000Z","msg":"1.義不容情（1989）<br />\n丁有健丁有康兩兄弟都係賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、害撚死阿敏阿華、最後丁有健害撚死埋親生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n震撼指數 ：5星<br />\n<br />\n2.大時代（1994）<br />\n劉青雲正仆街、搞到郭藹明最後死老豆、好心著雷劈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 丁蟹同班仔都係賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n震撼指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n3.美味情緣（2000）<br />\n林峯出道作、楊千嬅當時幾可愛、陳慧珊吳啟華、陣容不錯、輕鬆小品、笑中有淚、青春可人。<br />\n推介指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n4.忠奸人（2015）<br />\n郭晉安的奸樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、正邪界線模糊、郭晉安除左阿旺外的代表作、另外還有致命復活一併推介。<br />\n推介指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n5.我和殭屍有個約會（2000）<br />\n馬小玲的長腿JJable<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,支那人沒有一個是無辜的。ATV經典劇集。<br />\n推介指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n6.烈火雄心1、2（唔推介3）（1997、2004左右）<br />\n第一輯屋邨情懷、第二輯張可頤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、王喜的代表作<br />\n推介指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n7.金裝四大才子（1997？1998？）<br />\n陣容超級豪華、張家輝、關詠荷、波比、林家棟、文頌嫻<br />\n、好笑、輕輕鬆鬆的古裝長劇<br />\n希望tvb重播<br />\n想睇指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n8.TVB的穿越劇之最：尋秦記（2001）<br />\n比較擔心電影版會變屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 羨慕項少龍有咁多女人鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最愛鄔家大小姐<br />\n百看不厭指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n9.武俠劇-雪山飛狐（1999）<br />\n以前TVB製作武俠劇是有水準、大陸製的武俠劇會覺得好假、聽聞拍武俠劇的主角要俾金庸先生過目首肯先拍得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 選雪山飛狐係因為阿佘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要再睇其他的武俠片先評價到<br />\n想重播指數：5星<br />\n<br />\n10.衝上雲霄1（ 唔好睇2同電影版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)（2003）<br />\n捧出吳卓羲、Bosco ,葉璇、陳鍵鋒、馬明、遺憾阿Belle沒法同Sam哥一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仆街胡囧囧執左隻19 triangle 累人累乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nTVB神枱經典<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c899a77496f4905cd57187fd491f8308e5117682","tid":1960741,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:41:25.000Z","msg":"大冬瓜"},{"pid":"275ca9a12d414a32c45f7ecaf34eb36d8f505c9b","tid":1960741,"uid":15070,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:42:53.000Z","msg":"衝上雲霄1<br />\n溏心2<br />\nOncall 1<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f620cc032838a5fdd6ffadf79ffe3e6ceeab45","tid":1960741,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:44:52.000Z","msg":"On call 36小時1 （2走下坡）<br />\n最近睇on call重播、俾魚頭戀吸引左、魚仔的細心、慢慢令到一件頭沉船、對戀愛勇敢追求、女追男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又不會施加壓力、又有錢女又有學問又有性格。楊怡gfable <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <